Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.52,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我的朋友们 今天是狂欢节 "油腻星期二"{\r英文}\NThat's right, my friends, it's Mardi Gras, Fat Tuesday!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.52,注解,,0,0,0,,{\a6}又称"忏悔节" 基督教大斋期前的最后一个狂欢节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:20.89,中文,,0,0,0,,是时候放松一下了{\r英文}\NTime to cut it loose,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:21.92,中文,,0,0,0,,释放自己{\r英文}\Nget the Devil out ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:23.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我想将最热烈的欢呼{\r英文}\NI want to send a big shout-out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:27.03,中文,,0,0,0,,献给今晚的主办人 Hamilton市长{\r英文}\Nto my man, our host this evening, Mayor Hamilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:28.89,中文,,0,0,0,,上来这儿吧 市长先生{\r英文}\NCome on up here, Mr. Mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.73,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿{\r英文}\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:32.70,中文,,0,0,0,,你好啊 John Cleary{\r英文}\NHere he is-- John Cleary!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:36.10,中文,,0,0,0,,你们好吗{\r英文}\NHow you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:37.90,中文,,0,0,0,,耶{\r英文}\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:39.27,中文,,0,0,0,,我们都知道{\r英文}\NAll right, well, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:41.74,中文,,0,0,0,,纽约有跨年夜{\r英文}\NNew York has New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:44.34,中文,,0,0,0,,波士顿的圣帕特里克节{\r英文}\NAnd Boston's St. Pat's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.71,中文,,0,0,0,,有它的魅力{\r英文}\Nhas its charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:48.41,中文,,0,0,0,,但是没有人{\r英文}\NBut no one,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:50.32,中文,,0,0,0,,没有一个人{\r英文}\Nno one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.38,中文,,0,0,0,,比我们更懂得{\r英文}\Nknows how to party
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:54.05,中文,,0,0,0,,聚会狂欢{\r英文}\Nlike we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:55.39,中文,,0,0,0,,我说的对吗{\r英文}\NAm I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:57.26,中文,,0,0,0,,新奥尔良{\r英文}\NNew Orleans!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:01:00.06,中文,,0,0,0,,John Cleary{\r英文}\NJohn Cleary!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:02.69,中文,,0,0,0,,Tom 你是一个幸运的人{\r英文}\NTom, you are a lucky man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:04.13,中文,,0,0,0,,你是我的幕僚长{\r英文}\NYou're my chief of staff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:06.46,中文,,0,0,0,,还娶了这样的尤物{\r英文}\Nand you're married to this divine creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.47,0:01:08.17,中文,,0,0,0,,啊哈{\r英文}\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:09.90,中文,,0,0,0,,市长先生 你人真好{\r英文}\NOh, Mr. Mayor, you are too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:12.04,中文,,0,0,0,,这个城市爱你 Doug{\r英文}\NMm-hmm. The city loves you, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:17.01,中文,,0,0,0,,呃{\r英文}\NAh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:19.11,中文,,0,0,0,,裙子真好看{\r英文}\NNow, that is some dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:20.35,中文,,0,0,0,,魔鬼只在晚上出来{\r英文}\NDevils only night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:21.61,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯哼{\r英文}\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:24.78,中文,,0,0,0,,就像奥斯卡·王尔德说的{\r英文}\NWell, like Oscar Wilde always said:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:24.78,注解,,0,0,0,,{\a6}英国作家与艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:27.92,中文,,0,0,0,,"我可以抗拒一切 除了诱惑"{\r英文}\N"I can resist everything except... temptation."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:27.92,注解,,0,0,0,,{\a6}出自《Lady Windermere’s Fan》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:34.66,中文,,0,0,0,,又勾搭了一个吗{\r英文}\NIs that a new one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:36.03,中文,,0,0,0,,是的女士{\r英文}\NYes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:37.86,中文,,0,0,0,,确保他能在一小时内回来{\r英文}\NJust make sure he's back in an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:39.00,中文,,0,0,0,,和游行国王握手{\r英文}\Nto shake the parade king's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:39.00,注解,,0,0,0,,{\a6}狂欢节前会选出"国王"和"王后"站着游行彩车上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:40.10,中文,,0,0,0,,明白{\r英文}\NCopy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:42.97,中文,,0,0,0,,MONO要休息一会儿{\r英文}\NMONO's taking a breather.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.97,0:01:44.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我的人为我订了一个房间{\r英文}\NMy people keep a room for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:46.50,中文,,0,0,0,,就在那儿{\r英文}\NIt's right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:48.34,中文,,0,0,0,,哦{\r英文}\NOh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:50.84,中文,,0,0,0,,那有什么刺激的{\r英文}\NWhere's the sin in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:54.38,中文,,0,0,0,,唔{\r英文}\NMmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:56.15,中文,,0,0,0,,激将法{\r英文}\NA dare?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:57.08,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 我喜欢你{\r英文}\NOoh, I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:59.75,中文,,0,0,0,,-嗯 -好吧{\r英文}\N- Yeah. - Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.54,中文,,0,0,0,,哥们儿 你把电动发声器打开{\r英文}\NMan，it's a good thing you done up in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:20.07,注解,,0,0,0,,{\a6}第二季第五集提到过这个特别的老式机器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:20.07,中文,,0,0,0,,真是太好了{\r英文}\Nopening up the Tru-tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.24,中文,,0,0,0,,谢了兄弟{\r英文}\NOh, thanks, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.34,中文,,0,0,0,,为了我妈妈{\r英文}\NHad to breathe some life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:25.14,中文,,0,0,0,,我也得让这儿重获生机{\r英文}\Nback into the place for my mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:27.28,中文,,0,0,0,,-她一定会为你骄傲的 -谢谢{\r英文}\N- Oh, she'd really be proud of you. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:29.01,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 King 外面有一个送酒的男人{\r英文}\NHey, King, there's a guy out back that needs you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:30.42,中文,,0,0,0,,需要你签收货单{\r英文}\Nto sign for a liquor delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:32.25,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢{\r英文}\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.35,中文,,0,0,0,,失陪一下{\r英文}\NExcuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:34.35,中文,,0,0,0,,我们会为你罩住场的{\r英文}\NWe got it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:35.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你们会的{\r英文}\NI know you got it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:37.06,中文,,0,0,0,,我们继续这个派对{\r英文}\NLet's keep this party going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:39.22,中文,,0,0,0,,让我们尽情狂欢吧{\r英文}\NLet's get down and dirty up in here.
